<paragraph blockId="16.[151,1436,151,536]" pageId="16" pageNumber="17">
<emphasis bold="true" box="[199,321,439,464]" pageId="16" pageNumber="17">Diagnosis.</emphasis>
Recognizable by the black posteromedian part of tergite 
<quantity box="[1009,1058,439,464]" metricMagnitude="-2" metricUnit="m" metricValue="5.08" pageId="16" pageNumber="17" unit="in" value="2.0">2 in</quantity>
combination with the unsulcate scutellum.
</paragraph>
